author: lundblad
msg: Write merge conflict markers in the encoding of the current locale instead of
UTF8.
* subversion/libsvn_diff/diff_file.c
(svn_diff3__file_output_baton_t): Add comment about the encoding of four
string members.
(svn_diff_file_output_merge): Store the conflict marker strings in the locale
encoding in the baton.

author: brane
msg: Queries about binary packages should be sent to the users@ list, not
the dev@ list. And I'm heartily sick of getting private mails about
those packages.
* www/project_packages.html: Change instructions for posting questions
about binary packages in general, and for Win32 in particular.

author: maxb
msg: Fix include dependency generation in the presence of multiple include files
with the same basename.
* build/generator/gen_base.py (IncludeDependencyProcessor):
Do not rely on basenames being unique.
